Package: promptdown
Title: Literate Programming for LLM Prompt Composition.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Tomasz", "Kalinowski", , "tomasz@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A framework for composing prompts through literate programming. It uses knitr and ellmer to enable language model interactions where users can fully see and compose the full context sent to LLMs.
